    </teiHeader> <facsimile> <graphic url="1894_AS_RBH_2_00003.jpeg"/> <graphic url="1894_AS_RBH_2_00004.jpeg"/> <graphic url="1894_AS_RBH_2_00005.jpeg"/> <graphic url="1894_AS_RBH_2_00006.jpeg"/> </facsimile> <text type="letter"> <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1894_AS_RBH_2_00005"/>Herrn Dr. <hi rend="latintype">Richard Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb213" type="place">Ischl</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb766" type="place">Egelmoos 22</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1894_AS_RBH_2_00003"/>Lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>1) <rs ref="#pmb39539" type="person"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb39541" subtype="implied">Bolgar</rs></rs> geht eben unter Kreuzband ab.</p><p>2.) an <rs ref="#pmb18523" type="person">P. Horn</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chrieb ich, weil <rs ref="#pmb40227" type="org">Schenker</rs> immer be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>etzt i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t und das telefoniren mich nervös macht. Ich bat ihn, Ihnen direct<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ofort zu antworten.</p><p>3.) <rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Bahr</rs> werde ich morgen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>prechen.</p><p>4.) <rs ref="#pmb12618" type="person">Adele S.</rs> wohnt <rs ref="#pmb717" type="place">Opernring 19</rs>.</p><p>5.) Der <rs type="work" ref="#pmb40039" subtype="implied">Artikel</rs> der <rs ref="#pmb12183" type="person">Marholm</rs> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr werthvoll be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>onders. – Hie<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s »<rs ref="#pmb40039" type="work">Ein Märchen</rs>« und be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chäftigt<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich nach 1 ½ Seiten allg. Einleitung auf 2 ½ Seiten <pb facs="1894_AS_RBH_2_00004"/>mit mir. – (Be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tellt; Sie kriegen ihn da<c rendition="#gemination-n"/>)</p><p>6.) Verge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Sie nicht mir den Stock, welcher in Ihrer Hand<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o elegant wird, nach <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs> zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chicken.</p><p>7.) Glücklicher! –</p><closer>Herzliche Grüße Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer><p><date>9. Sept. 94</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>.</p></div></body> </text></TEI>